claim: The Youtube channel Epic Rap Battles of History has more than 13.3 million subscribers .
truth: As of May 2016 , it is the 20th most subscribed channel on YouTube with over 13.4 million subscribers and over 3 billion total video views .

claim: The Founder hints that the McDonald brothers should have received over $ 500 million annually , on royalties .
truth: An epilogue reveals that the McDonald brothers were never paid their royalties , which could have been in the area of $ 100 million a year.

claim: More than 190 countries and territories around the world had confirmed coronavirus cases by March 22 , 2020 .
truth: As of 22 March , more than 337,000 cases of COVID-19 have been reported in over 180 countries and territories , resulting in more than 14,400 deaths and 96,000 recoveries .

claim: China had registered more than 12,030 positive coronavirus cases by February 1 , 2020 .
truth: As of 1 February 2020 , approximately 12,038 cases have been confirmed , including in every province-level division of China .

claim: Less than 423,500 cases of coronavirus have been confirmed in more than 190 countries and territories .
truth: As of 25 March , more than 423,000 cases of COVID-19 have been reported in more than 190 countries and territories , resulting in more than 18,900 deaths and more than 109,000 recoveries .

claim: There were more than 390,000 COVID-19 cases worldwide by March 24 , 2020 .
truth: As of 24 March , more than 391,000 cases of COVID-19 have been reported in more than 190 countries and territories , resulting in more than 16,700 deaths and more than 102,000 recoveries .

claim: The state of Assam has confirmed a total of 32 positive cases of Covid-19 including 1 death as of 14 April 2020 .
truth: The state has confirmed a total of 32 positive cases of Covid-19 including 1 death as of 13 April 2020.The cause of Covid-19 outbreak in Assam is due to the people who attended the religious congregation of Tablighi Jamaat at Nizamuddin Markaz and did not reported the authorities after their return to Assam .

claim: More than 486,000 COVID-19 cases worldwide had been confirmed by March 26 , 2020 , including more than 117,000 recovered patients and about 22,000 deaths .
truth: As of 26 March , more than 479,000 cases of COVID-19 have been reported in over 190 countries and territories , resulting in approximately 21,500 deaths and more than 115,000 recoveries .

claim: Less than 60,100 cases have been confirmed , including in every province-level division of China .
truth: As of 13 February 2020 , 60,017 cases have been confirmed ( 8,047 serious ) , including in every province-level division of China , but official figures may not have counted a large number of people who have yet to be detected .

claim: Less than 128,500 people have recovered from COVID-19 from over 190 countries and territories as of March 27 , 2020 .
truth: As of 27 March , more than 559,000 cases of COVID-19 have been reported in over 190 countries and territories , resulting in approximately 25,200 deaths and more than 128,000 recoveries .

claim: In less than 200 countries , there have been less than 31,000 COVID-19 related deaths .
truth: more than 664,000 cases of COVID-19 have been reported in around 200 countries and territories , resulting in more than 30,800 deaths .

claim: Jong-hoon left F.T . Island in 2019 due to his involvement in the Burning Sun scandal .
truth: On March 14 , 2019 , Jong-hoon left the band and retired from the entertainment industry after involvement in a group chat in which some members shared videos of sexual activities recorded without the consent of the other party. ? oid=213 & aid=0001093008 Hong-gi began his mandatory military service on September 30 , 2019 , becoming the first F.T . Island member to enlist .

claim: The Formula One regulations requiring that the engines have 10 cylinders were put in place after 2000 .
truth: The rules between 2001 and 2005 stated that Formula One engines may be no more than 3 litres engine displacement and must have 10 cylinders .

claim: By November 2018 , more than 49 copies of the series Ahiru no Sora had been released in Japan .
truth: The first volume was released on May 17 , 2004 and as of March 16 , 2018 , forty-nine volumes have been released in Japan by Kodansha .

claim: As of March 20th , there were more than 87,500 recoveries in over 170 countries .
truth: As of 20 March , more than 245,000 cases of COVID-19 have been reported in over 170 countries and territories , resulting in more than 10,000 deaths and 88,000 recoveries .
